pageContext.claim: “Former FBI top lawyer James Baker just admitted involvement in FISA Warrant and further admitted there were IRREGULARITIES in the way the Russia probe was handled. They relied heavily on the unverified Trump ‘Dossier’ paid for by the DNC & Clinton Campaign, & funded through a... ...big Crooked Hillary law firm, represented by her lawyer Michael Sussmann (do you believe this?) who worked Baker hard & gave him Oppo Research for ‘a Russia probe.’ This meeting, now exposed, is the subject of Senate inquiries and much more. An Unconstitutional Hoax. @FoxNews”
pageContext.analysis: Several federal judges have upheld the legality of the special counsel's investigation into Russia and the Trump campaign. Although Trump dismisses the dossier compiled by Christopher Steele, some parts have been verified. Little is known about the episode Trump references involving Baker, since he appears to be referencing Fox News's reporting on Baker's non public testimony to the House.
